LUT KT HP (Association Rules) vi FP-Growth

Tm mi lin h 'nu-th' gia cc yu t tai nn

Mc tiu: p dng thut ton FP-Growth khm ph cc lut kt hp (association rules) gia cc yu t gy tai nn giao thng, nhm tm ra nhng mi lin h "nu-th" c ngha.

Phng php:

  • Thut ton FP-Growth tm tp ph bin (frequent itemsets)
  • To lut kt hp vi cc ch s: Support, Confidence, Lift
  • Lc cc lut c ngha thc tin

D liu:

  • 14 yu t c s h tng (boolean)
  • Temperature (3 mc: COLD/NORMAL/HOT)
  • Visibility (3 mc: LOW/MEDIUM/HIGH)
  • Hour (4 thi on: NIGHT/MORNING/AFTERNOON/EVENING)
  • Is_Weekend (boolean)

4. Ri rc ha cc c trng lin tc

Chuyn i cc c trng lin tc v thi gian thnh cc category ph hp vi Association Rules:

  • Temperature: 3 bins (COLD < 50F, NORMAL 50-80F, HOT > 80F)
  • Visibility: 3 bins (LOW < 2mi, MEDIUM 2-5mi, HIGH > 5mi)
  • Hour: 4 thi on (NIGHT 0-6h, MORNING 6-12h, AFTERNOON 12-18h, EVENING 18-24h)
  • Is_Weekend: Boolean (Th 7 hoc Ch nht)
In[10]:

6. p dng thut ton FP-Growth

FP-Growth (Frequent Pattern Growth) l thut ton hiu qu tm tp ph bin (frequent itemsets) m khng cn to candidate sets nh Apriori.

Tham s:

  • min_support = 0.005 (0.5%): Mt tp item xut hin t nht 0.5% s giao dch mi c coi l ph bin
In[13]:
import time

# Tham s cho FP-Growth
min_support = 0.005  # 0.5% - tp item xut hin t nht 0.5% s giao dch

print(f"ang chy FP-Growth vi min_support = {min_support} ({min_support*100}%)...")
print(f"Ngng ti thiu: {int(min_support * len(df_binary)):,} giao dch\n")

start_time = time.time()

# p dng FP-Growth
frequent_itemsets = fpgrowth(df_binary, min_support=min_support, use_colnames=True)

end_time = time.time()

print(f" Hon thnh trong {end_time - start_time:.2f} giy")
print(f" Tm thy {len(frequent_itemsets):,} tp ph bin (frequent itemsets)")

# Thm ct length (s lng items trong mi itemset)
frequent_itemsets['length'] = frequent_itemsets['itemsets'].apply(lambda x: len(x))

# Thng k theo  di
print("\nPhn b theo  di itemsets:")
length_counts = frequent_itemsets['length'].value_counts().sort_index()
for length, count in length_counts.items():
    print(f"  {length}-itemsets: {count:,}")

# Hin th top 20 frequent itemsets c support cao nht
print("\n" + "="*80)
print("TOP 20 FREQUENT ITEMSETS C SUPPORT CAO NHT:")
print("="*80)
top_itemsets = frequent_itemsets.nlargest(20, 'support')
for idx, row in top_itemsets.iterrows():
    items = ', '.join(sorted(row['itemsets']))
    print(f"Support: {row['support']:.4f} ({row['support']*100:5.2f}%) | Items: {{{items}}}")

7. To lut kt hp (Association Rules)

T cc frequent itemsets, to ra cc lut kt hp dng "Nu A Th B" vi cc ch s:

  • Support: Tn sut xut hin ca c A v B
  • Confidence: Xc sut B xut hin khi A xut hin (P(B|A))
  • Lift: Mc tng cng ca lut so vi ngu nhin (Lift > 1: c tng quan dng)

Tham s:

  • metric = "confidence": Sp xp theo confidence
  • min_threshold = 0.4: Confidence ti thiu 40%
  • lift > 1.5: Ch gi cc lut c lift > 1.5 (tng quan mnh)
In[14]:
# Tham s cho Association Rules
min_confidence = 0.4  # 40%
min_lift = 1.5

print("ang to Association Rules...")
print(f"  - Metric: confidence")
print(f"  - Min confidence: {min_confidence} ({min_confidence*100}%)")
print(f"  - Min lift: {min_lift}\n")

start_time = time.time()

# To lut kt hp
rules = association_rules(frequent_itemsets, metric="confidence", min_threshold=min_confidence)

# Lc theo lift
rules_filtered = rules[rules['lift'] > min_lift].copy()

end_time = time.time()

print(f" Hon thnh trong {end_time - start_time:.2f} giy")
print(f" To c {len(rules):,} lut kt hp")
print(f" Sau khi lc (lift > {min_lift}): {len(rules_filtered):,} lut\n")

# Sp xp theo lift gim dn
rules_filtered = rules_filtered.sort_values('lift', ascending=False).reset_index(drop=True)

# Thm ct antecedents_str v consequents_str  d c
rules_filtered['antecedents_str'] = rules_filtered['antecedents'].apply(lambda x: ', '.join(sorted(x)))
rules_filtered['consequents_str'] = rules_filtered['consequents'].apply(lambda x: ', '.join(sorted(x)))

# Thng k tng quan
print("="*80)
print("THNG K TNG QUAN V CC LUT:")
print("="*80)
print(f"Support:    Min = {rules_filtered['support'].min():.4f}, Max = {rules_filtered['support'].max():.4f}, Mean = {rules_filtered['support'].mean():.4f}")
print(f"Confidence: Min = {rules_filtered['confidence'].min():.4f}, Max = {rules_filtered['confidence'].max():.4f}, Mean = {rules_filtered['confidence'].mean():.4f}")
print(f"Lift:       Min = {rules_filtered['lift'].min():.4f}, Max = {rules_filtered['lift'].max():.4f}, Mean = {rules_filtered['lift'].mean():.4f}")

print("\n" + "="*80)
print("TOP 30 LUT KT HP MNH NHT (theo Lift):")
print("="*80)

top_rules = rules_filtered.head(30)
for idx, row in top_rules.iterrows():
    print(f"\nLut #{idx+1}:")
    print(f"  NU:  {{{row['antecedents_str']}}}")
    print(f"  TH:  {{{row['consequents_str']}}}")
    print(f"  Support:    {row['support']:.4f} ({row['support']*100:5.2f}%)")
    print(f"  Confidence: {row['confidence']:.4f} ({row['confidence']*100:5.2f}%)")
    print(f"  Lift:       {row['lift']:.4f}")
    print(f"  {'-'*76}")

fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(16, 12))

# Ly top 30 lut
top_30 = rules_filtered.head(30).copy()

# To labels cho trc y
y_labels = []
for idx, row in top_30.iterrows():
    antecedent = row['antecedents_str'][:30] + '...' if len(row['antecedents_str']) > 30 else row['antecedents_str']
    consequent = row['consequents_str'][:30] + '...' if len(row['consequents_str']) > 30 else row['consequents_str']
    y_labels.append(f"{antecedent}  {consequent}")

# V cc metric
y_pos = np.arange(len(top_30))
width = 0.25

bars1 = ax.barh(y_pos - width, top_30['support']*100, width, label='Support (%)', alpha=0.8, color='skyblue')
bars2 = ax.barh(y_pos, top_30['confidence']*100, width, label='Confidence (%)', alpha=0.8, color='lightcoral')
bars3 = ax.barh(y_pos + width, top_30['lift'], width, label='Lift', alpha=0.8, color='lightgreen')

ax.set_yticks(y_pos)
ax.set_yticklabels(y_labels, fontsize=8)
ax.invert_yaxis()
ax.set_xlabel('Gi tr', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')
ax.set_title('Top 30 Lut Kt Hp Mnh Nht (theo Lift)', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold', pad=20)
ax.legend(loc='lower right', fontsize=10)
ax.grid(axis='x', alpha=0.3, linestyle='--')

# Thm gi tr ln bars
for bars in [bars1, bars2, bars3]:
    for bar in bars:
        width_val = bar.get_width()
        if width_val > 0:
            ax.text(width_val, bar.get_y() + bar.get_height()/2, 
                   f'{width_val:.1f}', ha='left', va='center', fontsize=7)

plt.tight_layout()

8.2. Network Graph - Mi quan h gia cc Items

In[17]:
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(18, 14))

# Ly top 20 lut  v network (trnh qu phc tp)
top_rules_network = rules_filtered.head(20)

# To directed graph
G = nx.DiGraph()

# Thm edges t antecedents n consequents
for idx, row in top_rules_network.iterrows():
    for antecedent in row['antecedents']:
        for consequent in row['consequents']:
            # Thm edge vi weight l lift
            if G.has_edge(antecedent, consequent):
                # Nu edge  tn ti, cp nht weight bng gi tr ln hn
                G[antecedent][consequent]['weight'] = max(G[antecedent][consequent]['weight'], row['lift'])
                G[antecedent][consequent]['confidence'] = max(G[antecedent][consequent]['confidence'], row['confidence'])
            else:
                G.add_edge(antecedent, consequent, weight=row['lift'], confidence=row['confidence'])

# V network
pos = nx.spring_layout(G, k=2, iterations=50, seed=42)

# V nodes
node_sizes = [G.degree(node) * 500 for node in G.nodes()]
nx.draw_networkx_nodes(G, pos, node_size=node_sizes, node_color='lightblue', 
                       alpha=0.8, ax=ax, edgecolors='black', linewidths=2)

# V edges vi  dy theo lift
edges = G.edges()
weights = [G[u][v]['weight'] for u, v in edges]
confidences = [G[u][v]['confidence'] for u, v in edges]

# Normalize weights cho  dy edge
max_weight = max(weights) if weights else 1
edge_widths = [3 * (w / max_weight) for w in weights]

# V edges vi mu theo confidence
edge_colors = confidences
nx.draw_networkx_edges(G, pos, width=edge_widths, alpha=0.6, 
                       edge_color=edge_colors, edge_cmap=plt.cm.Reds,
                       arrows=True, arrowsize=20, arrowstyle='-|>',
                       connectionstyle='arc3,rad=0.1', ax=ax)

# V labels
labels = {}
for node in G.nodes():
    # Rt gn label nu qu di
    label = node.replace('INFRA_', '').replace('TEMP_', 'T_').replace('VIS_', 'V_').replace('HOUR_', 'H_')
    labels[node] = label

nx.draw_networkx_labels(G, pos, labels, font_size=9, font_weight='bold', ax=ax)

ax.set_title('Network Graph - Mi quan h gia cc yu t tai nn (Top 20 lut)', 
             fontsize=14, fontweight='bold', pad=20)
ax.axis('off')

# Thm colorbar cho edge colors
sm = plt.cm.ScalarMappable(cmap=plt.cm.Reds, norm=plt.Normalize(vmin=min(confidences), vmax=max(confidences)))
sm.set_array([])
cbar = plt.colorbar(sm, ax=ax, orientation='vertical', pad=0.01, shrink=0.8)
cbar.set_label('Confidence', fontsize=10, fontweight='bold')

# Thm ch thch
legend_text = " Kch thc node: S lng kt ni\n  dy edge: Lift (mc  tng quan)\n Mu edge: Confidence ( tin cy)"
ax.text(0.02, 0.98, legend_text, transform=ax.transAxes, fontsize=10,
        verticalalignment='top', bbox=dict(boxstyle='round', facecolor='wheat', alpha=0.5))

plt.tight_layout()
plt.savefig(output_dir / 'association_network_graph.png', dpi=300, bbox_inches='tight')
print("  lu: association_network_graph.png")
plt.show()

  lu: association_network_graph.png

# m tn sut xut hin ca mi item trong cc lut (c antecedents v consequents)
item_counts = {}

for idx, row in rules_filtered.iterrows():
    # m t antecedents
    for item in row['antecedents']:
        item_counts[item] = item_counts.get(item, 0) + 1
    # m t consequents
    for item in row['consequents']:
        item_counts[item] = item_counts.get(item, 0) + 1

# Chuyn thnh DataFrame v sp xp
item_freq_df = pd.DataFrame(list(item_counts.items()), columns=['Item', 'Frequency'])
item_freq_df = item_freq_df.sort_values('Frequency', ascending=True)

# Ly top 20
top_items = item_freq_df.tail(20)

# V biu 
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 10))

# To mu gradient
colors = plt.cm.viridis(np.linspace(0.3, 0.9, len(top_items)))

# Rt gn tn items
labels = [item.replace('INFRA_', '').replace('TEMP_', 'T_').replace('VIS_', 'V_').replace('HOUR_', 'H_') 
          for item in top_items['Item']]

ax.set_yticks(range(len(top_items)))

             fontsize=14, fontweight='bold', pad=20)
ax.grid(axis='x', alpha=0.3, linestyle='--')

# Thm gi tr ln bars
for i, (bar, freq) in enumerate(zip(bars, top_items['Frequency'])):

10. Kt lun v ng dng Thc tin

Tm tt kt qu:

p dng thnh cng thut ton FP-Growth khm ph cc lut kt hp t d liu tai nn giao thng, tm ra cc mi lin h "nu-th" c ngha gia cc yu t gy tai nn.

Nhng pht hin chnh:

  1. V Thi gian:

    • Tai nn vo cc thi im khc nhau trong ngy c mu hnh c trng ring
    • Bui sng (HOUR_MORNING) v bui ti (HOUR_EVENING) c cc yu t tng quan khc nhau
    • Cui tun c mu hnh tai nn khc bit so vi ngy thng

  2. V Thi tit:

    • Tm nhn thp (VIS_LOW) c tng quan mnh vi nhiu yu t nguy him khc
    • Nhit cc oan (qu lnh hoc qu nng) tng nguy c tai nn
    • Cc iu kin thi tit kt hp vi nhau to ra nguy c cao hn

  3. V C s h tng:

    • n giao thng (Traffic_Signal), giao l (Junction), v v tr bng qua ng (Crossing) l nhng im nng
    • Cc yu t c s h tng thng xut hin cng nhau ti cc im tai nn
    • Bin bo giao thng c vai tr quan trng trong vic gim thiu tai nn

ng dng thc tin:

  1. Quy hoch Giao thng:

    • u tin ci thin c s h tng ti cc v tr c s kt hp nguy him ca nhiu yu t
    • Lp t thm n chiu sng ti cc khu vc c tm nhn thp
    • Tng cng bin bo cnh bo ti cc im c nhiu yu t nguy him kt hp

  2. D bo v Cnh bo:

    • Pht trin h thng cnh bo da trn s kt hp ca cc yu t
    • Cnh bo c bit khi c s kt hp ca thi tit xu + thi gian nguy him + c s h tng thiu an ton
    • Tng cng tun tra ti cc im c lut kt hp vi lift cao

  3. Gio dc An ton:

    • Tuyn truyn v cc t hp yu t nguy him c th
    • Hng dn li xe cch x l trong cc tnh hung kt hp nhiu yu t ri ro
    • Nng cao nhn thc v cc im en tai nn c c im ring

  4. Chnh sch Qun l:

    • Phn b ngun lc da trn u tin ca cc lut kt hp
    • Thit k cc bin php can thip nhm vo cc t hp yu t c th
    • nh gi hiu qu ca cc bin php an ton giao thng

Hn ch v Hng pht trin:

  1. Hn ch:

    • D liu ch phn nh mi tng quan, khng chng minh quan h nhn qu
    • Mt s lut c support thp c th khng ng tin cy cho ng dng rng ri
    • Cht lng d liu gc nh hng n chnh xc ca cc lut

  2. Hng pht trin:

    • Kt hp thm d liu v mt giao thng, loi xe, iu kin ng
    • p dng cc thut ton khc nh Apriori, ECLAT so snh kt qu
    • Phn tch theo vng a l c th tm cc lut a phng
    • Tch hp vi cc m hnh Machine Learning khc d on tai nn
